{ This is not very Benko-like, but clearly the best move here. } 3. Bf4
{ The Jobava Opening. The Georgian creative genius has played tons of games with this line, getting unexplored positions with chances to fight. I suggest to immediately strike against d4 again. }
3... c5 4. dxc5 d4 { is no good for White as } 5. Nb5 Qa5+ { fails miserably. }
