14... d6 15. Nc4 Bxc4 16. Qg4 g6 17. Qxc4 Nc6 18. Qf4 d5
{ Black is fine here. This has been played between GM Suat Atalik and GM Sergey Kasparov in 2016. Atalik is a well respected theoretician, while Kasparov is a Benko specialist. It's a good sign for our opening that a well prepared GM like Atalik did not get more out of the opening. }
