{ This initiates an amazing sequence, obviously found by the engine. } 15. Ra1
Qxb2 16. Qe4+ Be7 17. Rb1 Nc3 18. Qxe7+ Kxe7 19. Rxb2 Ra1+ 20. Bc1 Rxc1+ 21.
Kd2 Bxd5 22. Bxd5 Rxg1 23. Rxg1 Nxd5 24. Rb5 Rc8 25. Re1+ Kd6
{ And this endgame is probably equal, but still has some play left. } *

