{ This position is winning for Black with careful play. } 16. Ne5 Bxd3 17. Rxa8
Qxd5 18. Ra5 Be4 19. Qxd5 Bxd5 20. Rxc5 Be6
{ And White's initative is over, Black is winning easily now. } *

